  <original-body>I've added disable_authenticity_token option to the form helper. So now we can generate forms without authenticity_token tag. 
It is useful when we generate forms for some external resources like payments and billings where names of fields are often restricted so forms with authenticity_token are not valid.

Now we can write:

@@@
form_for(@survey, :disable_authenticity_token =&gt; true)
@@@

or:

@@@
form_tag('/', :disable_authenticity_token =&gt; true)
@@@</original-body>
